originalText.text:
Womens Health Services PC -

Beware of this center . Honestly one of the worst experiences I have had . First , it took a long time to get an appointment . I called many times before someone finally picked up.  Second, when I finally got in touch they said I can come in three months. My first appointment , I came in and the receptionist and a patient were arguing. Unprofessional. Then  I waited about 1 hour after my appointment until I was finally seen. The nurse was okay but I was told I had to come back for another appointment . No one will tell me what was the appointment for. When I came back i waited 2 hours and 30 minute . When the guy came they told me to sign some paperwork quickly so I can be seen. I didn’t even get a chance to read it. They said they were just going to take picture. Then out of no where the guy said they doing a procedure and I was in so much pain . There was no pain management at all or even permission ask to continue . I am sharing this with you so that you are aware. I feel I was wronged .  There are so many things that made this the worst experience of my life. Beware before making an appointment to go see Denise west . This place needs to be investigated for fraud. I doubt there was anything wrong with me to begin with . Beware and honestly make another decision there are plenty of other reputable and better centers.

originalText.text: Just go to planned parenthood this place is a WASTE OF TIME. Had to wait a month to make the appointment then another 2 months for the actual appointment just to show up and for them not to offer nexplanon removal even though I specifically asked for that when making my appointment and the nurse telling me "maybe we thought it was an IUD" how do you work at a womans clinic and make that mistake.

originalText.text: They said they would call me in a day or two to give me my results, and they haven’t called. I’ve been calling all morning today and no answer. Decided to come in person and they are closed!!!! When they’re supposed to be open today! How am I getting my results that are a follow up from an emergency room visit of my pregnancy!!!? ! I was supposed to get this information Monday and I’ve waited two days, today is Wednesday and I still won’t get my results?!! How carelesss!!! If I would’ve know this I would’ve not wasted my time coming here! And would’ve went somewhere they would actually care about my emergency!
